title: Yaki Udon Noodle Stir Fry | Tim Anderson
description:
With all kinds of crunchy vegetables, exotic Japanese ingredients, bacon and thick udon noodles, Tim Anderson's Yaki Udon is a truly satisfying, colourful and tasty dish that you have to try! This stir fry recipe is from Kitakyushu, where Tim lived when he developed his Japanese culinary expertise, and features in his book of authentic soul food - Nanban.
